testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.ElasticSearchIndexServiceSpec

testcase.name: View type : Invalid - Build a query that returns only non-embargoed records
View type: 'myrecords' and empty userId - Build a query that should return only non-embargoed records
View type: 'myrecords' and valid userId - Build a query that returns all records associated to the user.
View type: 'project' - if ala admin or project member >> show all records associated to the project
View type: 'project'- if logged in user >> show non embargoed records + records created by user
View type: 'project'- if unauthenticated user and valid project >> show non embargoed records.
View type: 'allrecords' - logged in users and ala admin >> show all records across the projects
View type: 'allrecords' - logged in users and not ala admin >> show embargoed records that user own or been a member of the projects
View type: 'allrecords', logged in users and not ala admin >> show embargoed records that user own
View type: 'allrecords' - unauthenticated user >> show only embargoed records across the projects.
View type: 'allrecords' - unauthenticated user >> show only embargoed records across the projects and attach the searchTerm
the include and exclude parameters are optional
